

=Bio=

Dr. Kenrick, Justin (UK). Research fellow  in social anthropology at the University of Edinburgh. He works with the Forest Peoples Programme to support Forest Peoples in Africa secure their rights, and also works on his local  community resilience initiative, PEDAL and the broader movement for resilience in Scotland through Holyrood 350.    


